<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11132</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们能休息一会儿吗？”一天八戒嘟囔着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>山路很长，他们已经走了一个早上了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25366</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的腿都疼了！”八戒大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29271</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>34028</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们过一会儿就休息。”唐僧说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>34029</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>38646</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>走着走着，他们听到了流水声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>38647</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那声音越来越大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“前面好像有条河。”悟净说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>50190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们绕过一个小山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>50191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>54905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，他们就到了河边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>54906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58913</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们怎么过河呢？”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它太宽了，我都看不到对岸。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62363</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>67514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳到空中，四处看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>67515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71033</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“附近有个村子。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71034</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那里可能会有船。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们走进了村子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>街上一个人都没有。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85363</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几个村民躲在门窗后面偷看他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85364</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89707</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人看上去都很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89708</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93383</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人正在井边打水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93384</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96397</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好！”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96398</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那个男人吓了一跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>水桶掉到了井里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104271</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他迅速转过身来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104272</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106378</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你......你是谁？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106379</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧上前一步。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111031</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我来自东土大唐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要去西天取经。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人放松了一点儿。“是这样啊！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122503</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要坐船过河。”八戒说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122504</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125722</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我没有船。”男人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125723</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128281</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“村子里有人可能有船。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>请跟我来。我给你们泡点儿茶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134046</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们可以叫我老陈。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134047</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧他们跟着老陈回了家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们在屋子里坐了下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146603</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老陈开始烧水泡茶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146604</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“为什么村民们看上去都是很害怕的样子？”唐僧问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159377</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老陈叹了口气坐下了。他哭了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159378</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“老陈。”唐僧说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你怎么了？是我说错话了吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165793</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170329</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是。”老陈一边哭，一边说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170330</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这村子里的日子实在太难过了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173915</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几年前，有个可怕的妖怪来到这里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178633</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他一直都对我们不好，现在情况更坏了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们每年要献给他一个孩子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191645</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果我们不照做，他就会毁了我们整个村子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191646</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197257</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天早上，我就必须......必须把我的儿子献出去！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197258</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201653</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老陈又开始大哭起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201654</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>207387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧瞪着悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>207388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“悟空！你为什么笑？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210127</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒摇摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216531</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他很残忍，师父。你念紧箍咒吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216532</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不用把孩子献出去。”悟空笑着说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他转身对老陈说：“我不是在笑你，老陈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是笑你很幸运。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232512</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天是你一生中最幸运的一天。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232513</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237761</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老陈扬起了眉毛问：“为什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237762</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242582</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可能从没听说过我。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242583</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我是美猴王孙悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>248782</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我曾打败过玉帝的天兵天将。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>248783</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>明天，我救你的儿子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255023</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是神仙吗？”老陈问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255024</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259609</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对，我是非常厉害的神仙。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259610</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>262767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把你的儿子带来。我要看看他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>262768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266731</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老陈出去了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>266732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，他带来了一个小男孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我的儿子。”老陈说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275698</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285905</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空绕着小男孩儿走了一圈，仔细看了看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285906</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292253</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，悟空交叉着双臂说：“我有办法了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292254</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，小男孩儿爬上了一个步辇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>304170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>四个村民抬着步辇走到了河边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>304171</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>311264</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们把步辇放在了地上，然后就跑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>311265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314649</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一切都很安静。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314650</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>318589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿一个人坐在步辇上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>318590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>323096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，河面出现了一团黑云。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>323097</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>327246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>云中出现一个长得很凶的妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>327247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>329563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的牙很尖。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>329564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336792</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>小男孩儿朝着妖怪笑了笑。“你好呀！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>